{
  "stem": "25938.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You were very, very weak, and you were about to die.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came to that time-- to that place and a Polish doctor told me to lay down, to count.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I counted to 12.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think I remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he operated-- operate on me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I feel like that-- that scar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And after the war, people told me, doctors told me they did a-- did a very good job.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So then, that-- that's how the Germans did these [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they-- they operate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They-- they-- they cured you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they sent to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They told me-- so I wanted-- after the operation, I knew I was alert.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I knew if-- I had to go to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If not, I'm dying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I-- I-- I says, are we allowed to go?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He says, no, you're not going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I took my-- I want to take to-- to get dressed.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "No, you're not-- not going to get-- to get dressed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You go like this, naked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Go to that number seven, block number seven.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's a barracks called number seven.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I knew that was a death block, the famous block seven.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I went to that-- to that block.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember it was, I think, in autumn time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I was-- I was without-- without clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No one was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a quiet, and abysmally quiet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a little-- a little bed-- a little, like a-- a stretcher, I think.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like near hospitals there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I laid down there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I felt so good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "People-- people didn't-- no one beat me up, I-- I-- I expected to be-- not to be beaten up there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was left alone by myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was there on that place.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
